        <h2>Coatings Built For <span class="hl">Orange County Weather</span></h2>
        <p>Winter Park's tree-lined streets and classic architecture deserve a finish that lasts. Our coating system protects brick, stucco, and wood siding from Florida's heat and rain while keeping the timeless curb appeal homeowners here are known for.</p>
        <p>For 30+ years, AWA Coatings has protected Winter Park's historic, character-rich homes near Park Avenue with a patented coating system engineered to defend against the elements year after year, no chips, no cracks, no peeling.</p>
        <div class="phero-cta" style="margin-top:6px">
          <a href="#quote" class="btn btn-primary">Get My Free Quote</a>
          <a href="/testimonials/" class="btn btn-teal">Read Reviews</a>
