<section class="bg2">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <div class="kicker">Why Winter Park Chooses AWA</div>
      <h2>A Finish That <span class="hl">Outlasts Paint</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card"><div class="why-ic">🛡️</div><h3>10x Thicker Than Paint</h3><p>Applied far thicker than ordinary paint to form a durable, waterproof, armor-like barrier that resists cracking and peeling on Winter Park exteriors.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card"><div class="why-ic">🌡️</div><h3>Cooler Walls, Lower Bills</h3><p>Our heat-reflective coating keeps walls up to 40° cooler during peak Florida summers, helping reduce cooling costs for Winter Park homeowners.*</p></div>
      <div class="why-card"><div class="why-ic">💧</div><h3>Waterproof &amp; Fire-Rated</h3><p>Waterproof protection against Orange County's humidity and storms, plus a Class A Fire Rating and powerful UV resistance.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card alt"><div class="why-ic">🔁</div><h3>End Constant Repainting</h3><p>Most homes need repainting every 5-7 years. Our system ends that cycle, saving Winter Park homeowners thousands over time.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card alt"><div class="why-ic">🎨</div><h3>Any Color, HOA-Approved</h3><p>From HOA-approved palettes to a fully custom look, our system can be applied to almost any exterior surface in Winter Park.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card alt"><div class="why-ic">📜</div><h3>Lifetime Warranty</h3><p>Backed by a lifetime transferable warranty against peeling, cracking, and premature failure, peace of mind paint can't offer.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

