      <h2>Winter Park Coating <span class="hl">Questions</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-wrap">
      <div class="faq"><h3><span class="q">Q.</span> Do you serve all of Winter Park?</h3><p>Yes, we provide exterior coating and house painting throughout Winter Park and the surrounding Orange County area, including Olde Winter Park, Hannibal Square, and nearby neighborhoods.</p></div>
      <div class="faq"><h3><span class="q">Q.</span> How is a coating different from regular paint?</h3><p>Traditional paint is a thin film that fades and peels in a few years. Our coating is applied up to 10x thicker, creating a waterproof, flexible, heat-reflective, fire-rated barrier built to protect for decades, backed by a lifetime warranty.</p></div>
      <div class="faq"><h3><span class="q">Q.</span> Will it lower my energy bills?</h3><p>Our heat-reflective coatings reflect Florida's heat instead of absorbing it, for up to 21.9% reduced cooling costs and up to 40% lower wall temperatures during peak Winter Park summers.*</p></div>
      <div class="faq"><h3><span class="q">Q.</span> Do you offer financing?</h3><p>Yes. Right now we're offering 50% off plus 0% interest for 12 months on exterior coating projects in Winter Park so you can protect your home and pay over time.</p></div>
      <div class="faq"><h3><span class="q">Q.</span> How do I get started?</h3><p>Call us at (407) 669-3261 or request a free quote to schedule a no-pressure consultation with a local Winter Park coating expert.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

